{"word":"G840 - αὐστηρός - austērós - ow-stay-ros' - Austere","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αὐστηρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">austērós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ow-stay-ros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Austere</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கடினமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"harsh of mind and manners, harsh, rough, rigid"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a (presumed) derivative of the same as <a href=\"#/G109 - ἀήρ - aḗr - ah-ayr'/109\">G109</a> (meaning <i>blown</i>); <i>rough</i> (properly as a <i>gale</i>), that is, (figuratively) <i>severe:</i> - austere.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}